  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Music and Art in Recovery Treatment of Teens Pilot</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Addiction among teens is of epidemic proportions  still growing and is across all demographics, incomes and geographic locations.  We all know a family who has lost a teen to death by suicide or overdose.  We can help!  This project will fund a pilot project using music and art in the recovery treatment of addicted teens to cement their recovery skills and help them explore feelings in a positive way.</narrative>
  </description>
